channel.title: [PI] Home Height Level
channel.description:
How do I change the Home Teleport's height level?
Like if I wanted [code] public static final int HOME_X = 1897; public static final int HOME_Y = 5356; [/code] to teleport me to a height level of 2, what would I add? :confused:

item.title: [PI] Home Height Level
item.dc:creator: @Impious_Lols Impious Lols
item.description:
@Impious_Lols wrote:

Or if you wanted to, you could just go to clicking buttons and make the home button like

case #### (home button): c.getPA().startTeleport(xxxx, yyyy, (height here), "modern"); break;
